		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">32.110</ph> Payment of subcontractors under cost-reimbursement prime contracts.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p class="- topic/p ">If the contractor makes financing payments to a subcontractor under a cost-reimbursement prime contract, the contracting officer should accept the financing payments as reimbursable costs of the prime contract only under the following conditions:</p>
			      <ol id="d2026e16" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2040e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The payments are made under the criteria in <xref href="FAR-i1082047.dita#i1082047"
                        base="i1082047"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpartÂ  32.5</xref> for customary progress payments based on costs, <xref href="FAR-i1083117.dita#i1083117"
                        base="i1083117"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.202-1</xref> for commercial item purchase financing, or <xref href="FAR-i1080969.dita#i1080969"
                        base="i1080969"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.1003</xref> for performance-based payments, as applicable.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2040e38" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If customary progress payments are made, the payments do not exceed the progress payment rate in <xref href="FAR-i1082067.dita#i1082067"
                        base="i1082067"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.501-1</xref>, unless unusual progress payments to the subcontractor have been approved in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1082080.dita#i1082080"
                        base="i1082080"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.501-2</xref>.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2040e53" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If customary progress payments are made, the subcontractor complies with the liquidation principles of <xref href="FAR-i1082368.dita#i1082368"
                        base="i1082368"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.503-8</xref>, <xref href="FAR-i1082371.dita#i1082371"
                        base="i1082371"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.503-9</xref>, and <xref href="FAR-i1082397.dita#i1082397"
                        base="i1082397"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.503-10</xref>.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2040e71" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            If performance-based payments are made, the subcontractor complies with the liquidation principles of <xref href="FAR-i1080976.dita#i1080976"
                        base="i1080976"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.1004</xref>(d).</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2040e83" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The subcontract contains financing payments terms as prescribed in this part.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
